{"tid":416804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴無理解僱 陳章萍索償35萬 無限期押後審理","createTime":"2017-09-28T05:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T06:34:58.000Z","uid":64694,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eae29f5bf2667c0f71eec30a886447cdfb2e36f0","tid":416804,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】被揭發有「影子學生」的屯門興德學校，被罷免的前校長陳章萍早前向勞工署投訴校方無理解僱，入稟要求學校賠償35萬元。勞資審裁處今開庭審理。署理主任審判官何慧縈指陳章萍仍有刑事調查在進行中，為免庭上的宣誓供詞成為入罪事項，並保障雙方利益，決定無限期押後審理，待雙方確認刑事程序完成，可申請恢復聆訊。陳章萍步出法院後，未有回應記者提問。（申索書編號：LBTC2814/2017）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wVToXpNBcgKIiYoPfNSNHA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170928a112545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwVToXpNBcgKIiYoPfNSNHA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170928a112545.jpg&h=fb2f82af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9f49045dece10fc19bf79e9b1eca2b40c1941b1","tid":416804,"uid":14816,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"死肥閪臉皮厚撚過啲脂肪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e8f506877a0056263e3476c9274220cc32a31c","tid":416804,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"佢仲係咁玩嘢想人地唔鋤佢其他罪"},{"pid":"2e602f6ee25a0ad61c64c90d42c344ccf16ec9e8","tid":416804,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:27:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ab59a3d15d4a537e21956e59198860103e978c","tid":416804,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"肥婆：學校仲差我好多餅卡，還番啲餅卡嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59507ad605fe297845689b782dc1e795572f6b3","tid":416804,"uid":134834,"like":0,"disli